data.description: NVESTOR ALERT! Welcome to 913 McFaddin Station Ct., a two-story traditional home located in the highly sought-after Rivers Landing Edge subdivision. Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home offers a spacious lot with plenty of privacy. The backyard is fully fenced, offering a secure and private outdoor space  Recently appraised at 295K,priced under recent appraisal for quick sale! Seller's Loan is an assumable loan, great opportunity to get favorable terms on interest rate, please contact the Listing Agent for details! Schedule an exclusive showing today!  Currently has 1 year lease in place starting Nov'23, great opportunity for a beautiful investment property UNDER recent appraised value!
